    {
      "type": "text", "id": "guard_t",
      "x": 140, "y": 896, "width": 940, "height": 80,
      "text": "Guardrails  (safety is load-bearing)\n• dryRun (default true) gates all GitHub writes/pushes      • risk:\"high\" forces escalate regardless of action\n• fast-forward-only push, aborts if branch moved             • SerialQueue per repo  ·  per-thread auto-fix limit\n• never act on a GitHub-resolved Thread (re-checked just before action)   • amend_pr_body is drafted, never auto-applied\n• gh CLI is the only GitHub surface — no in-app token",
      "originalText": "Guardrails  (safety is load-bearing)\n• dryRun (default true) gates all GitHub writes/pushes      • risk:\"high\" forces escalate regardless of action\n• fast-forward-only push, aborts if branch moved             • SerialQueue per repo  ·  per-thread auto-fix limit\n• never act on a GitHub-resolved Thread (re-checked just before action)   • amend_pr_body is drafted, never auto-applied\n• gh CLI is the only GitHub surface — no in-app token",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#334155", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
